  • public class CreatePaymentTokenRequest
extends com.worldpay.library.webservices.services.ServiceRequest
    Used to create Payment Token Request, token received in Token Response.

    The following values must be present on ALL Create Payment Token Requests:

    • setAddTovault(boolean)

      • Must specify payment medium Check OR Card.

      • setCard(Card)
      • setCheck(Check)
